\v 8 ISiriya\x + 37.36.\x* izakuwa-ke ngenkemba engeyisiyo yomuntu olamandla\x + 2.9.\x*, lenkemba engeyisiyo yomuntukazana\x + 2.9.\x* izayiqeda; kodwa izabalekela inkemba\x + Jobe 19.29.\x*, lamajaha ayo abe yizibhalwa.
\v 9 Izakwedlulela\x + 37.37.\x* \add e\add*dwal\add eni\add* layo ngokwesaba, leziphathamandla zayo zesabe uphawu\x + 11.10. Eks. 17.15.\x*, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, omlilo wayo useZiyoni\x + 24.15.\x*, lesithando sayo siseJerusalema\x + Hlab. 21.9. Mal. 4.1.\x*.